{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9dcf7df2cf","title":"毛泽东给江青有关武斗问题的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a789a59f17","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":4,"articleId":"9dcf7df2cf","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"书信","id":"2a70b5d939","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"dd68a2a705","type":"title","text":"毛泽东给江青有关武斗问题的信","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9dcf7df2cf","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d6a5230683","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9dcf7df2cf","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cab8b99f16","type":"paragraph","text":"夺枪问题并不严重，90％以上的枪是在许多有右倾思想的军区、军分区、人武部手里，一部分流入老保组织，左派得的不过百分之一、二、三而已。此事宜重新计划，每省都应开人武部以上各级干部的会，少者一、二百人，多者四、五百人，大省应到千人左右。在北京开，实是训练班。半年之内争取办好此事，否则一年也可。再则应大量武装左派，例如一个省武装左派5万支枪，全国也不过一百多万支枪。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9dcf7df2cf","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9b30abd68a","type":"paragraph","text":"如此则左派声势大振，右派气焰就可压下去了。但应在条件成熟的地方先做，条件不成熟的省则应缓行。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9dcf7df2cf","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fec08684be","type":"paragraph","text":"以上两个问题提请林、周及文革各同志从长讨论。如同少剑波的嘱咐：既要勇敢，又要谨慎。你的意见是对的。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9dcf7df2cf","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"96e13f0203","type":"paragraph","text":" \t润之　8月4日","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9dcf7df2cf","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}